msgstr "如需更多資訊或想要為此擴充套件評分，請前往 Cinnamon Spices 網站。"

#: 5.4/res/preferences.glade:2810
msgid "Cinnamon Dynamic Wallpaper at Cinnamon Spices Website"
msgstr "Cinnamon Spices 網站上的 Cinnamon 動態桌布"

